      "text": "Devfolio\n\nSign Up -> Email -> Verification Mail (OTP, Link)\nHey Hey!!\n297778 is the code to verify your email.\n\nOr you can click on this button to verify your email instantly:\n\nVerify email\nBoth the code and the button are good for 30 minutes. If they have expired, you can always request again.\n\nNever Stop Building,\nTeam Devfolio",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Devfolio\n\nSign Up -> Email -> Verification Mail (OTP, Link)\nHey Hey!!\n297778 is the code to verify your email.\n\nOr you can click on this button to verify your email instantly:\n\nVerify email\nBoth the code and the button are good for 30 minutes. If they have expired, you can always request again.\n\nNever Stop Building,\nTeam Devfolio",
